ST10-ST10-001 normal.name: Trafalgar Law (001)
ST10-ST10-001 normal.description: [Activate:Main] [Once Per Turn] DON!! -3 (You may return the specified number of DON!! cards from your field to your DON!! deck.): Place up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 3000 power or less at the bottom of the owner's deck, and play up to 1 Character card with a cost of 4 or less from your hand.

ST10-ST10-002 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (002)
ST10-ST10-002 normal.description: [Activate:Main] [Once Per Turn] If you have 0 DON!! cards on your field or 8 or more DON!! cards on your field, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and set it as active.

ST10-ST10-003 normal.name: Eustass"Captain"Kid (003)
ST10-ST10-003 normal.description:
[Your Turn] If you have 4 or more Life cards, give this Leader -1000 power.
[When Attacking] DON!! -1 (You may return the specified number of DON!! cards from your field to your DON!! deck.): This Leader gains +2000 power during this turn.

ST10-ST10-004 normal.name: Sanji
ST10-ST10-004 normal.description: [On Play] If your opponent has a Character with 5000 or more power, this Character gains [Rush] during this turn. (This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)

ST10-ST10-005 normal.name: Jinbe
ST10-ST10-005 normal.description: [DON!! x1] [When Attacking] Give up to 1 of your opponent's Characters -2000 power during this turn.

ST10-ST10-006 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (006)
ST10-ST10-006 normal.description:
[Rush] (This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)
[Once Per Turn] When your opponent activates a [Blocker], K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 8000 power or less.

ST10-ST10-007 normal.name: Killer
ST10-ST10-007 normal.description: [Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When a DON!! card on your field is returned to your DON!! deck, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's rested Characters with a cost of 3 or less.

ST10-ST10-008 normal.name: Shachi & Penguin
ST10-ST10-008 normal.description: [On Play] If you have 3 or less DON!! cards on your field, add up to 2 DON!! cards from your DON!! deck and rest them.

ST10-ST10-009 normal.name: Jean Bart
ST10-ST10-009 normal.description: [On Play] (1) (You may rest the specified number of DON!! cards in your cost area.): Add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and set it as active.

ST10-ST10-010 normal.name: Trafalgar Law (010)
ST10-ST10-010 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Play] DON!! -1 (You may return the specified number of DON!! cards from your field to your DON!! deck.): If your opponent has 7 or more cards in their hand, trash 2 cards from your opponent's hand.

ST10-ST10-011 normal.name: Heat
ST10-ST10-011 normal.description: [Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When a DON!! card on your field is returned to your DON!! deck, this Character gains +2000 power until the start of your next turn.

ST10-ST10-012 normal.name: Bepo
ST10-ST10-012 normal.description: [On Play] / [When Attacking] If your opponent has more DON!! cards on their field than you, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.

ST10-ST10-013 normal.name: Eustass"Captain"Kid (013)
ST10-ST10-013 normal.description: [On Play] / [When Attacking] DON!! -1 (You may return the specified number of DON!! cards from your field to your DON!! deck.): Up to 1 of your Leader gains +1000 power until the start of your next turn.

ST10-ST10-014 normal.name: Wire
ST10-ST10-014 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[Once Per Turn] When a DON!! card on your field is returned to your DON!! deck, draw 1 card and trash 1 card from your hand.

ST10-ST10-015 normal.name: Gum-Gum Giant Sumo Slap
ST10-ST10-015 normal.description: [Counter] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +2000 power during this battle, and K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 2000 power or less.

ST10-ST10-016 normal.name: Gum-Gum Kong Gatling
ST10-ST10-016 normal.description:
[Main] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 7000 power or less.
[Trigger] Up to 1 of your Leader gains +1000 power until the end of your next turn.

ST10-ST10-017 normal.name: Punk Vise
ST10-ST10-017 normal.description:
[Main] Rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 2 or less, and add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.
[Trigger] Add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and set it as active.
